# Title: Suspicious Base64 Encoded User-Agent
# Author: Nasreddine Bencherchali (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2023-05-04
# Level: medium
# Description: Detects suspicious encoded User-Agent strings, as seen used by some malware.
# MITRE Tactic: Command and Control
# Tags: attack.command-and-control, attack.t1071.001
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/web/proxy_generic/proxy_ua_base64_encoded.yml

"c-useragent" IN ("Q2hyb21l*", "QXBwbGVXZWJLaX*", "RGFsdmlr*", "TW96aWxsY*")